---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import TimelineDiagram from '../components/TimelineDiagram.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Readiness Process" description="Step-by-step GDPR readiness process, sprint timeline, and deliverables for technology companies.">
  <section class="content">
    <h1>Readiness Process</h1>

    <p>The readiness sprint is a focused engagement that produces everything you need to demonstrate GDPR accountability with confidence: a complete ROPA, lawful basis documentation, DPIA methodology, and a clear remediation roadmap.</p>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Sprint Timeline</h2>
      <p>The engagement follows four phases, each building on the outputs of the previous one.</p>
      <TimelineDiagram />
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Phase Details</h2>

      <div class="phase-detail">
        <h3>1. Intake &amp; Scoping <span class="phase-duration">Week 1</span></h3>
        <p>We start by understanding your processing landscape, data flows, and compliance context.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Processing activity inventory</strong> &mdash; catalog all processing activities across the organization</li>
          <li><strong>Lawful basis mapping</strong> &mdash; identify the legal basis relied on for each processing activity</li>
          <li><strong>Third-party processor review</strong> &mdash; map all processors and sub-processors handling personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Cross-border transfer assessment</strong> &mdash; identify all international data flows and current transfer mechanisms</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="phase-detail">
        <h3>2. Assessment <span class="phase-duration">Week 2&ndash;3</span></h3>
        <p>We evaluate your current data protection posture against GDPR requirements.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>ROPA development</strong> &mdash; build or validate a comprehensive Record of Processing Activities</li>
          <li><strong>DPIA evaluation</strong> &mdash; identify processing activities requiring impact assessments and review existing DPIAs</li>
          <li><strong>Data subject rights workflow review</strong> &mdash; assess response procedures for all right types against 30-day timelines</li>
          <li><strong>International transfer mechanism assessment</strong> &mdash; evaluate adequacy of SCCs, BCRs, and other transfer safeguards</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="phase-detail">
        <h3>3. Outputs <span class="phase-duration">Week 3&ndash;4</span></h3>
        <p>We deliver the artifacts that define your path to GDPR accountability.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Gap register and remediation plan</strong> &mdash; every gap ranked by risk with owners and timelines</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy notice templates</strong> &mdash; GDPR-compliant notices for employees, customers, and website visitors</li>
          <li><strong>DPIA methodology framework</strong> &mdash; reusable methodology for conducting future impact assessments</li>
          <li><strong>Processor agreement templates</strong> &mdash; Article 28-compliant data processing agreement language</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="phase-detail">
        <h3>4. Follow-on <span class="phase-duration">Ongoing</span></h3>
        <p>After the readiness sprint, continued support ensures sustained compliance.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>ROPA maintenance</strong> &mdash; ongoing updates as processing activities change</li>
          <li><strong>DPIA updates for new processing</strong> &mdash; impact assessments for new products, features, and vendor relationships</li>
          <li><strong>Transfer impact assessments</strong> &mdash; ongoing evaluation of international transfer mechanisms</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Sprint Deliverables</h2>
      <p>Every readiness sprint produces these minimum deliverables:</p>
      <div class="deliverables-grid">
        <div class="deliverable-item">Record of Processing Activities (ROPA)</div>
        <div class="deliverable-item">Lawful basis documentation</div>
        <div class="deliverable-item">Data subject rights procedures</div>
        <div class="deliverable-item">DPIA methodology framework</div>
        <div class="deliverable-item">International transfer assessment</div>
        <div class="deliverable-item">Processor agreement review</div>
        <div class="deliverable-item">Privacy notice templates</div>
        <div class="deliverable-item">Remediation roadmap</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section cta-section">
      <h2>Start Your Readiness Sprint</h2>
      <p>Most companies complete the readiness sprint in 3&ndash;4 weeks. The result is a clear, actionable plan to demonstrate GDPR accountability.</p>
      <a href="/about" class="cta-button">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .phase-detail {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .phase-detail h3 {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .phase-duration {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 0.125rem 0.5rem;
  }

  .phase-detail ul {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .deliverables-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .deliverable-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-heading);
  }

  .deliverable-item::before {
    content: '\2713';
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .deliverables-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
